# =====================================================================
# ENVIRONMENT-SPECIFIC CONFIGURATION
# =====================================================================
# Development settings: see .env.development
# Production settings: see .env.production
#
# The app automatically loads the correct file based on NODE_ENV:
# - NODE_ENV=development → loads .env.development
# - NODE_ENV=production → loads .env.production
